General Assembly Proposed Bill No. 15
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 305
Referred to Committee on APPROPRIATIONS
Introduced by:
SEN. KISSEL, 7th Dist.
AN ACT CONCERNING FUNDING FOR ELDERLY NUTRITION.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 That six million dollars be appropriated to the Department of Aging
2 and Disability Services, from the General Fund, for the fiscal year
3 ending June 30, 2027, for elderly nutrition.
Statement of Purpose:
To increase funding for elderly nutrition.
